('47','1','1','video','4k-istanbul-turkey-urban-documentary-film-cities-of-the-world','4K Istanbul, Turkey - Urban Documentary Film - Cities of the World','Are you dreaming about vacation? Let\'s go to one of the most beautiful cities in Turkey, Istanbul! This is a great advantage - which you shouldn\'t miss. Discover amazing aerial views of Turkey\'s history-rich Istanbul in 4K 10-bit color resolution!','{\"source\":\"youtube\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/nJRa1PwwvKI\",\"content\":\"<p><span class=\\\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\">Are you dreaming about vacation? Let\'s go to one of the most beautiful cities in Turkey, Istanbul! This is a great advantage - which you shouldn\'t miss. Discover amazing aerial views of Turkey\'s history-rich Istanbul in 4K 10-bit color resolution! This urban documentary film will bring you to the most beautiful region of the city, Sultanahmet (<\\/span>3:58<span class=\\\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\">), show lots of ships floating on the Bosporus (<\\/span>9:58<span class=\\\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\">), the palace of the Ottoman sultans, Dolmabahce Saray (<\\/span>6:45<span class=\\\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\">), and series of other famous places on the seaside. You can enjoy the magical view of the Bosporus, sea strait between the Black Sea and the Marmara Sea, its charming lighthouses, such as Maiden\'s Tower (<\\/span>14:14<span class=\\\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\">), and unwind. Explore typical architecture, streets, and bridges from above! Listen to the pleasant background melodies and feel like flying over Istanbul cityscapes with the seagulls&hellip; You will have an opportunity to walk along the alluring promenade (<\\/span>7:54<span class=\\\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\">) with flower shops, take a look at a lot of local fishermen (<\\/span>8:34<span class=\\