('91','1','2','video','4k-istanbul-turkey-urban-documentary-film-cities-of-the-world','4K Istanbul, Turkey - Urban Documentary Film - Cities of the World','Are you dreaming about vacation? Let\'s go to one of the most beautiful cities in Turkey, Istanbul! This is a great advantage - which you shouldn\'t miss. Discover amazing aerial views of Turkey\'s history-rich Istanbul in 4K 10-bit color resolution!','{\"source\":\"youtube\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/nJRa1PwwvKI\",\"content\":\"<p><span class=\\\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\">Are you dreaming about vacation? Let\'s go to one of the most beautiful cities in Turkey, Istanbul! This is a great advantage - which you shouldn\'t miss. Discover amazing aerial views of Turkey\'s history-rich Istanbul in 4K 10-bit color resolution! This urban documentary film will bring you to the most beautiful region of the city, Sultanahmet (<\\/span>3:58<span class=\\\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\">), show lots of ships floating on the Bosporus (<\\/span>9:58<span class=\\\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\">), the palace of the Ottoman sultans, Dolmabahce Saray (<\\/span>6:45<span class=\\\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\">), and series of other famous places on the seaside. You can enjoy the magical view of the Bosporus, sea strait between the Black Sea and the Marmara Sea, its charming lighthouses, such as Maiden\'s Tower (<\\/span>14:14<span class=\\\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\">), and unwind. Explore typical architecture, streets, and bridges from above! Listen to the pleasant background melodies and feel like flying over Istanbul cityscapes with the seagulls&hellip; You will have an opportunity to walk along the alluring promenade (<\\/span>7:54<span class=\\\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\">) with flower shops, take a look at a lot of local fishermen (<\\/span>8:34<span class=\\\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\">), stroll along local streets with atmospheric caf&eacute;s and restaurants, and even take a virtual boat tour on the Bosporus. Experience Istanbul at day and at night. Learn more about Turkish national delicacies during your evening walk and dive into the maze of the Grand Bazaar, one of the largest and oldest covered markets in the world (<\\/span>33:19<span class=\\\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\">). This documentary film will show you Istanbul in all its glory: explore this city from the shore, water, or from the sky with our team! Turn on this 4K 10-bit color video and plan your next trip to this fascinating Turkish city! <\\/span><\\/p>\"}','','{\"meta_title\": \"4K Istanbul, Turkey - Urban Documentary Film - Cities of the World\", \"meta_keywords\": null, \"meta_description\": \"Are you dreaming about vacation? Let\'s go to one of the most beautiful cities in Turkey, Istanbul! This is a great advantage - which you shouldn\'t miss. Discover amazing aerial views of Turkey\'s history-rich Istanbul in 4K 10-bit color resolution!\"}','c.62ba117b8e569,c.62ba117b90b90','','{\"featured_image\":\"https:\\/\\/img.youtube.com\\/vi\\/nJRa1PwwvKI\\/maxresdefault.jpg\",\"slider_image\":null}','{\"breaking\":\"1\"}','','16','RZtSmH','2022-07-11 22:06:00','2022-07-20 16:30:37','2022-09-06 21:05:35','','published','all');

